# bin/ is intentionally NOT excluded so the raven binary ships in the VSIX. The
# Tier 3 sidecar is excluded, though: VS Code users run alongside their local R
# install, so Tier 1 already resolves their installed packages — the broad
# CRAN/Bioconductor floor isn't needed and would only bloat the VSIX.
